OL,3,CGuernsey politicians propose GST
OL,4,Cintroduction for fourth time
OL,6,FGuernsey politicians have proposed
OL,7,Fintroducing a 5% goods and services
OL,8,Ftax to the island instead of an income
OL,9,Ftax increase.
OL,11,FDeputy Peter Roffey is bringing
OL,12,Fforward the amendment for Guernsey's
OL,13,F2025 Budget to introduce GST to the
OL,14,Fisland, replacing the planned 2%
OL,15,Fincrease in income tax.
OL,17,FProposals would instead include a new
OL,18,F15% tax band for earnings up to
OL,19,F#30,000, meaning income tax will drop
OL,20,Fby #900 for most people.
