OL,3,CGuernsey politicians propose GST
OL,4,Cintroduction for fourth time
OL,6,FIt's the fourth time GST has been
OL,7,Fdebated this political term, having
OL,8,Fbeen voted down three times before.
OL,10,FIt is understood that Deputy Peter
OL,11,FFerbrache will be seconding the motion.
OL,13,FDeputy Roffey says GST is more
OL,14,Fattractive than an income tax, with
OL,15,Fthis fourth attempt more likely to
OL,16,Fpass as the States of Guernsey must
OL,17,Feffectively choose between introducing
OL,18,FGST or increasing income tax.
