OL,10,Facross the year or about #22 a week.
OL,12,FHowever, some residents have taken to
OL,13,Fsocial media to voice their concerns.
OL,15,FOne commenter says: "We are in a big
OL,16,Fproblem (...) take some action now for
OL,17,Fa short 2-year period.
