OL,6,FOne more says "Is anyone else sick of
OL,7,Ffighting the same battles again and
OL,8,Fagain? It's our money - shouldn't we
OL,9,Fhave some say at least into whether
OL,10,Fwe're going to be allowed a decent
OL,11,Flife?"
OL,13,FThere were some shows of support with
OL,14,Fone resident explaining: "GST is the
OL,15,Ffairest way. This way everyone pays.
OL,16,FThe more you spend, the more you
OL,17,Fcontribute."
