OL,3,CGuernsey politicians propose GST
OL,4,Cintroduction for fourth time
OL,6,FNo, it's not 'Groundhog Day', even
OL,7,Fthough it might seem like it. GST is
OL,8,Fback on the table... again, and it's
OL,9,Fposed an alternative to income tax
OL,10,Frises... again.
OL,12,FThis is the fourth time this term that
OL,13,Fa goods and services tax has been
OL,14,Fbrought to the table and the second
OL,15,Ftime Deputy Lyndon Trott has tried to
OL,16,Fget a 2p on the pound increase in
OL,17,Fincome tax through the States.
