OL,3,CGuernsey politicians propose GST
OL,4,Cintroduction for fourth time
OL,6,FLast year, it was Deputy Peter
OL,7,FFerbrache's version of P&R that
OL,8,Fproposed a 5% GST and its failure to
OL,9,Fgain support saw him ousted as Chief
OL,10,FMinister and replaced by Deputy Trott.
OL,12,FNow it's Deputy Peter Roffey,
OL,13,Fsupported by Deputy Ferbrache, who is
OL,14,Fpitching the same 5% GST from 2027.
OL,16,FThe two options are coming from
OL,17,Fincreasingly desperate States, who are
OL,18,Fstruggling to tackle a deficit by the
OL,19,Fend of this year of #24 million.
