OL,3,CGuernsey politicians propose GST
OL,4,Cintroduction for fourth time
OL,6,FA temporary income tax increase will
OL,7,Fraise roughly #56 million over the
OL,8,Fnext two years, and introducing GST
OL,9,Fcould bring in #50 million a year
OL,10,Fpermanently.
OL,12,FIt's widely understood that Guernsey
OL,13,Fmust generate more income to protect
OL,14,Fagainst changing demographics and
OL,15,Fincreasing healthcare costs. The
OL,16,Fisland simply doesn't have enough
OL,17,Fmoney and the two biggest levers
OL,18,Favailable are GST and income tax.
